title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Rediscovering and redefining who you are in relationships becomes a key focus now. Whether youre single or coupled, step out of your comfort zone and engage in discussions that center on how to share more of your life while still keeping your own distinct identity. Treat all interpersonal engagements as opportunities for mutual growth while the transformational Scorpio New Moon takes place in your 7th House of Partnerships. Author Neale Donald Walsch wrote, The purpose of relationship is not to have another who might complete you, but to have another with whom you might share your completeness. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
